: \"\\\"I am a very positive person most of the time so there is not too much thinking 'what if', because it does not change the outcome and it does not change the fact that I could still give my best effort and get an Olympic silver.\\\"\", \"from\": 1003, \"to\": 1231, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"a very positive person\", \"from\": 1009, \"to\": 1031}, {\"ngram\": \"the time\", \"from\": 1040, \"to\": 1048}, {\"ngram\": \"too much thinking\", \"from\": 1065, \"to\": 1082}, {\"ngram\": \"the outcome\", \"from\": 1121, \"to\": 1132}, {\"ngram\": \"the fact\", \"from\": 1156, \"to\": 1164}, {\"ngram\": \"my best effort\", \"from\": 1189, \"to\": 1203}, {\"ngram\": \"an Olympic silver\", \"from\": 1212, \"to\": 1229}]}, {\"sentence\": \"But Peaty will never know what he could have achieved without the illness, and the possibility of competing at a fourth Games at LA 2028 is a carrot dangling tantalisingly in front of him.\", \"from\": 1233, \"to\": 1421, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Peaty\", \"from\": 1237, \"to\": 1242}, {\"ngram\": \"the illness\", \"from\": 1295, \"to\": 1306}, {\"ngram\": \"the possibility\", \"from\": 1312, \"to\": 1327}, {\"ngram\": \"a fourth Games\", \"from\": 1344, \"to\": 1358}, {\"ngram\": \"LA\", \"from\": 1362, \"to\": 1364}, {\"ngram\": \"a carrot\", \"from\": 1373, \"to\": 1381}, {\"ngram\": \"front\", \"from\": 1408, \"to\": 1413}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"You want to end on a Games that you have got all your best cards to your chest,\\\" he said.\", \"from\": 1423, \"to\": 1513, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"a Games\", \"from\": 1443, \"to\": 1450}, {\"ngram\": \"all your best cards\", \"from\": 1469, \"to\": 1488}, {\"ngram\": \"your chest\", \"from\": 1492, \"to\": 1502}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"I feel like in Paris I did not have any cards to my chest, I was just going out there and racing.\", \"from\": 1514, \"to\": 1612, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1530, \"end\": 1535, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"score\": 0.9999999977972038, \"rank\": 2.2026892130327282e-09, \"text\": \"Paris\", \"types\": [\"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"any cards\", \"from\": 1551, \"to\": 1560}, {\"ngram\": \"my chest\", \"from\": 1564, \"to\": 1572}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"I know there is a better performance in there but, whether that's worth the four-year hike onMount Everest, that's a different question.\", \"from\": 1614, \"to\": 1751, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"a better performance\", \"from\": 1631, \"to\": 1651}, {\"ngram\": \"the four-year hike\", \"from\": 1687, \"to\": 1705}, {\"ngram\": \"onMount Everest\", \"from\": 1706, \"to\": 1721}, {\"ngram\": \"a different question\", \"from\": 1730, \"to\": 1750}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"LA would be incredible to be there, it's just obviously a long way away and I am sure plenty's going to change between now and then.\\\"\", \"from\": 1753, \"to\": 1887, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"LA\", \"from\": 1754, \"to\": 1756}, {\"ngram\": \"plenty\", \"from\": 1840, \"to\": 1846}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Central to Peaty's decision could be whether the 50m breaststroke, in which he is the world record holder and a three-time world champion, is included in the programme.\", \"from\": 1889, \"to\": 2057, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Peaty's decision\", \"from\": 1900, \"to\": 1916}, {\"ngram\": \"the world record holder\", \"from\": 1971, \"to\": 1994}, {\"ngram\": \"a three-time world champion\", \"from\": 1999, \"to\": 2026}, {\"ngram\": \"the programme\", \"from\": 2043, \"to\": 2056}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Another question mark surrounds Peaty's training, with his long-term coach Mel Marshall now working in Australia.\", \"from\": 2059, \"to\": 2172, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2162, \"end\": 2171, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Australia_national_cricket_team\", \"score\": 0.7413869445879455, \"rank\": 0.3487444175893235, \"text\": \"Australia\", \"types\": [\"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\", \"Q12973014\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Australia_national_cricket_team\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Australia_national_cricket_team\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Another question mark\", \"from\": 2059, \"to\": 2080}, {\"ngram\": \"Peaty's training\", \"from\": 2091, \"to\": 2107}, {\"ngram\": \"his long-term coach\", \"from\": 2114, \"to\": 2133}, {\"ngram\": \"Mel Marshall\", \"from\": 2134, \"to\": 2146}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Whether they could find a way of making things work remains to be seen, with Peaty saying: \\\"It's something we have not discussed.\", \"from\": 2174, \"to\": 2303, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"a way\", \"from\": 2198, \"to\": 2203}, {\"ngram\": \"things\", \"from\": 2214, \"to\": 2220}, {\"ngram\": \"Peaty\", \"from\": 2251, \"to\": 2256}, {\"ngram\": \"something\", \"from\": 2271, \"to\": 2280}]}, {\"sentence\": \"If she wanted to take that on, I am sure she would, but I do not know what that is going to look like.\", \"from\": 2304, \"to\": 2406, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"The decision needs to be made within the next year or year and a half and then we go from there.\", \"from\": 2408, \"to\": 2505, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"The decision\", \"from\": 2409, \"to\": 2421}, {\"ngram\": \"the next year\", \"from\": 2446, \"to\": 2459}, {\"ngram\": \"year\", \"from\": 2463, \"to\": 2467}, {\"ngram\": \"a half\", \"from\": 2472, \"to\": 2478}]}, {\"sentence\": \"I know there is a better performance in there but, whether that's worth the four-year hike on Mount Everest, that's a different question.\", \"from\": 2507, \"to\": 2644, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"a better performance\", \"from\": 2523, \"to\": 2543}, {\"ngram\": \"the four-year hike\", \"from\": 2579, \"to\": 2597}, {\"ngram\": \"Mount Everest\", \"from\": 2601, \"to\": 2614}, {\"ngram\": \"a different question\", \"from\": 2623, \"to\": 2643}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"I will always be in touch with Mel, she's like my third parent, so we will see where those conversations take us, but at the moment I am just staying active, staying ready, staying fairly fit and not fat, and trying to make the most of each day.\\\"\", \"from\": 2646, \"to\": 2893, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"touch\", \"from\": 2667, \"to\": 2672}, {\"ngram\": \"Mel\", \"from\": 2678, \"to\": 2681}, {\"ngram\": \"my third parent\", \"from\": 2694, \"to\": 2709}, {\"ngram\": \"those conversations\", \"from\": 2732, \"to\": 2751}, {\"ngram\": \"us\", \"from\": 2757, \"to\": 2759}, {\"ngram\": \"the moment\", \"from\": 2768, \"to\": 2778}, {\"ngram\": \"each day\", \"from\": 2883, \"to\": 2891}]}, {\"sentence\": \"For now, Peaty is focusing on other projects, including his AP Race swimming brand, while he also took part in Amazon's Black Friday Week Show, highlighting the retailer's offers.\", \"from\": 2895, \"to\": 3074, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2955, \"end\": 2957, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Associated_Press\", \"score\": 0.9999999686847336, \"rank\": 1.0506440649236579e-08, \"text\": \"AP\", \"types\": [\"Q4830453\", \"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Associated_Press\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Associated_Press\"}, {\"begin\": 3006, \"end\": 3012, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Amazon_Music\", \"score\": 0.9963359317441209, \"rank\": 0.0027531943044126323, \"text\": \"Amazon\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Amazon_Music\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Amazon_Music\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Peaty\", \"from\": 2904, \"to\": 2909}, {\"ngram\": \"other projects\", \"from\": 2925, \"to\": 2939}, {\"ngram\": \"part\", \"from\": 2998, \"to\": 3002}, {\"ngram\": \"the retailer's offers\", \"from\": 3052, \"to\": 3073}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"It was really fun,\\\" said Peaty.\", \"from\": 3076, \"to\": 3108, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Peaty\", \"from\": 3102, \"to\": 3107}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"Going through our purchase history and Black Friday and all the deals you can get.\", \"from\": 3109, \"to\": 3192, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"our purchase history\", \"from\": 3124, \"to\": 3144}, {\"ngram\": \"Black Friday\", \"from\": 3149, \"to\": 3161}, {\"ngram\": \"all the deals\", \"from\": 3166, \"to\": 3179}]}, {\"sentence\": \"That was my first time being in that kind of environment.\", \"from\": 3193, \"to\": 3250, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"my first time\", \"from\": 3202, \"to\": 3215}, {\"ngram\": \"that kind\", \"from\": 3225, \"to\": 3234}, {\"ngram\": \"environment\", \"from\": 3238, \"to\": 3249}]}, {\"sentence\": \"I am always open to doing new things.\\\"\", \"from\": 3251, \"to\": 3289, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"new things\", \"from\": 3277, \"to\": 3287}]}, {\"sentence\": \"While he has not spent much time in the pool recently, Peaty has been keeping fit by running, doingCrossFitand going to the gym.\", \"from\": 3291, \"to\": 3419, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"much time\", \"from\": 3314, \"to\": 3323}, {\"ngram\": \"the pool\", \"from\": 3327, \"to\": 3335}, {\"ngram\": \"Peaty\", \"from\": 3346, \"to\": 3351}, {\"ngram\": \"the gym\", \"from\": 3411, \"to\": 3418}]}, {\"sentence\": \"The change in exercise routine has been a challenge, with Peaty adding: \\\"I have really struggled with that but at the same time I am fortunate that I have got a lot of training in my body, my body's still relatively lean and I never have a problem with maintaining muscle.\", \"from\": 3421, \"to\": 3693, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"The change\", \"from\": 3421, \"to\": 3431}, {\"ngram\": \"a challenge\", \"from\": 3461, \"to\": 3472}, {\"ngram\": \"Peaty\", \"from\": 3479, \"to\": 3484}, {\"ngram\": \"the same time\", \"from\": 3535, \"to\": 3548}, {\"ngram\": \"a lot\", \"from\": 3580, \"to\": 3585}, {\"ngram\": \"training\", \"from\": 3589, \"to\": 3597}, {\"ngram\": \"my body\", \"from\": 3601, \"to\": 3608}, {\"ngram\": \"my body\", \"from\": 3610, \"to\": 3617}, {\"ngram\": \"a problem\", \"from\": 3659, \"to\": 3668}, {\"ngram\": \"muscle\", \"from\": 3686, \"to\": 3692}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"I miss every single day just having that sole purpose of being the fastest.\", \"from\": 3695, \"to\": 3771, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"that sole purpose\", \"from\": 3732, \"to\": 3749}]}, {\"sentence\": \"But with that comes high risk.\", \"from\": 3772, \"to\": 3802, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"high risk\", \"from\": 3792, \"to\": 3801}]}, {\"sentence\": \"As we have seen in the Olympics, you are increasing your odds every day, but if you have one bad day that could take your result out.\", \"from\": 3803, \"to\": 3936, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the Olympics\", \"from\": 3822, \"to\": 3834}, {\"ngram\": \"your odds\", \"from\": 3855, \"to\": 3864}, {\"ngram\": \"one bad day\", \"from\": 3892, \"to\": 3903}, {\"ngram\": \"your result\", \"from\": 3920, \"to\": 3931}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"Whereas, in most of life, you work every day and you get a little bit of validation and gratification along the way.\", \"from\": 3938, \"to\": 4055, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"life\", \"from\": 3959, \"to\": 3963}, {\"ngram\": \"a little bit\", \"from\": 3996, \"to\": 4008}, {\"ngram\": \"validation\", \"from\": 4012, \"to\": 4022}, {\"ngram\": \"gratification\", \"from\": 4027, \"to\": 4040}, {\"ngram\": \"the way\", \"from\": 4047, \"to\": 4054}]}, {\"sentence\": \"I do miss the training and the racing but at the 